In ''[[NetHack]]'', the letter '''Z''' serves the following purposes:

* {{white|z}} represents a [[Zruty (monster class)|zruty]], which is a [[monster class]] consisting only of the titular [[zruty]].

* {{white|Z}} represents a [[Zombie (monster class)|zombie]]:
** {{monsymlink|kobold zombie}}
** {{monsymlink|gnome zombie}}
** {{monsymlink|orc zombie}}
** {{monsymlink|dwarf zombie}}
** {{monsymlink|elf zombie}}
** {{monsymlink|human zombie}}
** {{monsymlink|ettin zombie}}
** {{monsymlink|giant zombie}}
** {{monsymlink|ghoul}}
** {{monsymlink|skeleton}}

* Press {{kbd|z}} to [[zap]] a wand.
* Press {{kbd|shift|z}} to zap a [[spell]] that you have learned.
* press {{kbd|ctrl|z}} to suspend NetHack if applicable - see [[^Z]] for more details.

==Variants==
===SLASH'EM===
[[SLASH'EM]] replaces the zruty monster class with the [[zouthern animal]]s for the {{white|z}} glyph, moving the zruty with the [[apelike creature]]s, and introduces new monsters that use the {{white|Z}} glyph:

* {{white|z}} "zouthern" animals:
** {{monsymlink|echidna}}
** {{monsymlink|platypus}}
** {{monsymlink|koala}}
** {{monsymlink|wombat}}
** {{monsymlink|Tasmanian devil}}
** {{monsymlink|wallaby}}
** {{monsymlink|wallaroo}}
** {{monsymlink|kangaroo}}
* {{white|Z}} undead:
** {{monsymlink|ghoul mage}}
** {{monsymlink|ghast}}
** {{monsymlink|ghoul queen}}
** {{monsymlink|gug}}
